                "invention-title": [
                    "Preparation method and application of chlorine-doped carbon dot modified carbon nitride material",
                    "氯掺杂碳点修饰氮化碳材料的制备方法及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a chlorine-doped carbon dot modified carbon nitride material as well as a preparation method and application thereof, and belongs to the technical field of photocatalyst materials. The preparation method comprises the following steps: by taking mulberry twig powder as a raw material, adding water for dispersing, then adding thionyl chloride, uniformly mixing, heating to 180-200 DEG C, keeping for 10-12 hours to prepare chlorine-doped carbon dots, filtering and purifying to obtain a chlorine-doped carbon quantum dot material marked as Cl-CQDs; the preparation method comprises the following steps: dissolving a certain amount of urea and Cl-CQDs powder, mixing, drying to remove moisture, and calcining the dried powder in a tubular furnace to obtain the chlorine-doped carbon dot modified carbon nitride material marked as Cl-CTCN. The preparation method is simple, convenient to operate, mild in reaction condition, low in raw material cost and suitable for large-scale industrial production. The Cl-CTCN disclosed by the invention has good photocatalytic performance and good reusability, can be applied to photocatalytic degradation of organic pollutants such as tetracycline, rhodamine B, methyl orange and the like and hydrogen production by photolysis of water, and has wide practicability."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氯掺杂碳点修饰氮化碳材料及其制备方法和应用，属于光催化剂材料技术领域。本发明以桑枝粉末为原料，加水分散后加入氯化亚砜，混匀，加热到180‑200℃保持10‑12h制备氯掺杂碳点，过滤、纯化即可得到氯掺杂碳量子点材料，记为Cl‑CQDs；取一定量尿素和Cl‑CQDs粉末溶解，混合，干燥去除水分，将干燥后的粉末置于管式炉中煅烧，得到氯掺杂碳点修饰氮化碳材料，标记为Cl‑CTCN。本发明的制备方法简单、操作方便、反应条件温和，原料成本低，适合大规模工业化生产。本发明的Cl‑CTCN具有良好的光催化性能，重复循环使用性好，可以应用到四环素、罗丹明B和甲基橙等有机污染物的光催化降解以及光解水产氢，具有广泛的实用性。"
                }
            ]
